sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy / Gateway API<br/>TLS Termination
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>4180/TCP HTTP
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Upstream as Upstream Application<br/>Configurable Port

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 1: OIDC Authentication (auth mode)
    Client->>Gateway: GET /protected-resource<br/>No auth cookie
    Gateway->>AuthProxy: Forward request
    AuthProxy-->>Client: 302 Redirect to /oauth2/start
    Client->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/start
    AuthProxy-->>Client: 302 Redirect to OIDC Provider<br/>with client_id, redirect_uri, PKCE
    Client->>OIDC: GET /authorize<br/>User credentials
    OIDC-->>Client: 302 Redirect to /oauth2/callback<br/>Authorization Code
    Client->>AuthProxy: GET /oauth2/callback?code=xxx
    AuthProxy->>OIDC: POST /token<br/>Client Credentials + Auth Code
    OIDC-->>AuthProxy: ID Token + Access Token
    AuthProxy-->>Client: Set-Cookie: _oauth2_proxy=...<br/>302 Redirect to original URL
    Client->>AuthProxy: GET /protected-resource<br/>Cookie: _oauth2_proxy
    AuthProxy->>Upstream: GET /protected-resource<br/>X-Remote-User, X-Remote-Groups
    Upstream-->>AuthProxy: 200 OK Response
    AuthProxy-->>Client: 200 OK Response

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 2: Kubernetes RBAC Authorization (rbac mode)
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Client->>RBACProxy: GET /resource<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: TokenReview: authenticated=true<br/>user=system:serviceaccount:ns:sa
    RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authorization.k8s.io/v1/subjectaccessreviews<br/>SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: SubjectAccessReview: allowed=true
    RBACProxy->>Upstream: GET /resource<br/>X-Remote-User, X-Remote-Groups
    Upstream-->>RBACProxy: 200 OK Response
    RBACProxy-->>Client: 200 OK Response

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 3: K8s Service Account Token (auth mode)
    Client->>AuthProxy: GET /api/endpoint<br/>Authorization: Bearer <SA Token>
    AuthProxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>AuthProxy: TokenReview: authenticated=true
    AuthProxy->>Upstream: GET /api/endpoint<br/>X-Remote-User, X-Remote-Groups
    Upstream-->>AuthProxy: 200 OK Response
    AuthProxy-->>Client: 200 OK Response
